text: Auguste Castille (12 May 1883 - 17 September 1971) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1971 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Elbeuf
